					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-634991#post-3591905</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-634991/scp-1905#post-3591905</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 14 Sep 2017 15:35:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Moist Spaghetti</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1387731</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's a gun that makes dinosaurs appear around you for you to shoot.<br /> How do I upvote this more than once?</p> <p>One little issue I noticed.</p> <blockquote> <p>.577 tyrannosaur round</p> </blockquote> <p>Tyrannosaur should be capitalized. Also, since the foundation uses the metric system, 14.9×76mm would be an accurate measurement as well. There's debate over which you should use, but I will angrily debate anyone who things &quot;14.9x76mm&quot; sounds cooler than &quot;.577 Tyrannosaur&quot;.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
